comments: The work load is EXTREME. A total overload of reading plus at least one paper every week. But she is a Great Teacher. I would take another one of her classes, just maybe not as many other classes at the same time.

She assigns a RIDICULOUS amount of reading, book/movie reports, research papers EVERY WEEK! Most of it would be fun, if it wasn\'t so overwhelming. Perhaps she thought her\'s was the only her students were taking for the semester.
